            "body": "Why not use sized integers for everything, including for formatting?\r\n```\r\nprintf(\"%+\"PRId64\"\\n\", some_int64_t);\r\n```\r\n... it looks weird, but it would be truthful to the intention.\r\n\r\nhttps://en.cppreference.com/w/c/types/integer",
